696
00:30:40,500 --> 00:30:42,040
 po snjegovima,

697
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:43,740
 po logorima bili.

698
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:45,220
 Neki ljudi su se borili

699
00:30:45,220 --> 00:30:46,280
 da bi stvorili ovu državu.

700
00:30:46,280 --> 00:30:47,480
 Pa vi toko ste dužni,

701
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:48,820
 mladi moji dragi,

702
00:30:48,820 --> 00:30:50,000
 da bar izađete

703
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:51,880
 jedan put u četiri godine

704
00:30:51,880 --> 00:30:52,980
